    QDIMACSBuilder
    stores information for the QDIMACSConverter an additional variable is a variable that is not part of the quantifiers (free, exists, forall) These are separated since they are added to an exists quantifier at the end
    QDIMACSConverter
    Class to convert a qbf formula to QDIMACS Requires a QDIMACSBuilder since the construction is not sequential Some metrics must be stored during construction and result assembly can only happen at the end (nb var and nb clauses for example)
    RandomCAFRootCompletionGenerator
    Returns root completions for a CAF (with no probability distribution) Therefore the random part is purely random
    RandomPCAFRootCompletionGenerator
    Returns random root completions for PCAF Therefore it computes the random completions according to the distribution of the completions.
